<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Note on Kaya Log</title><link>https://yshghid.github.io/docs/bioinformatics/note/</link><description>Recent content in Note on Kaya Log</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en-us</language><lastBuildDate>Sat, 31 Aug 2024 00:00:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://yshghid.github.io/docs/bioinformatics/note/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>[np분석] SARS-CoV-2 human protein interaction analysis</title><link>https://yshghid.github.io/docs/bioinformatics/note/note3/</link><pubDate>Sat, 31 Aug 2024 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://yshghid.github.io/docs/bioinformatics/note/note3/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="np분석-sars-cov-2-human-protein-interaction-analysis">
 [np분석] SARS-CoV-2 human protein interaction analysis
 &lt;a class="anchor" href="#np%eb%b6%84%ec%84%9d-sars-cov-2-human-protein-interaction-analysis">#&lt;/a>
&lt;/h1>
&lt;h2 id="human-ppi-network">
 Human ppi network
 &lt;a class="anchor" href="#human-ppi-network">#&lt;/a>
&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>&lt;strong>Network 다운로드&lt;/strong>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;a href="https://string-db.org/">STRING db&lt;/a>에 접속해서 download를 선택하고, organism of interest에 homo sapiens를 입력해준다.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/9a2b0abf-4cf4-4f29-99f5-32b04a79190b" alt="image" />&lt;/p>
&lt;p>이중에 protein.links.full.v12.0.txt.gz를 다운받아준다.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>cf) &lt;strong>Subscore 의미&lt;/strong> &lt;a href="https://string-db.org/cgi/info?sessionId=bEKyfCQ15Bqb&amp;amp;footer_active_subpage=scores">https://string-db.org/cgi/info?sessionId=bEKyfCQ15Bqb&amp;footer_active_subpage=scores&lt;/a>&lt;/p>
&lt;blockquote>
&lt;p>&lt;strong>The basic principle&lt;/strong>&lt;/p>
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>In STRING, each protein-protein interaction is annotated with one or more &amp;lsquo;scores&amp;rsquo;.&lt;/li>
&lt;li>Importantly, these scores do not indicate the strength or the specificity of the interaction. Instead, they are indicators of confidence, i.e. how likely STRING judges an interaction to be true, given the available evidence. All scores rank from 0 to 1, with 1 being the highest possible confidence. A score of 0.5 would indicate that roughly every second interaction might be erroneous (i.e., a false positive).&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;/blockquote>
&lt;blockquote>
&lt;p>&lt;strong>Transfer scores&lt;/strong>&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>[Data Sourcing] GISAID: Influenza sequence 받기</title><link>https://yshghid.github.io/docs/bioinformatics/note/data1/</link><pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://yshghid.github.io/docs/bioinformatics/note/data1/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="data-sourcing-gisaid-influenza-sequence-받기">
 [Data Sourcing] GISAID: Influenza sequence 받기
 &lt;a class="anchor" href="#data-sourcing-gisaid-influenza-sequence-%eb%b0%9b%ea%b8%b0">#&lt;/a>
&lt;/h1>
&lt;h2 id="0829">
 0829
 &lt;a class="anchor" href="#0829">#&lt;/a>
&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>GISAID 계정생성.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;a href="https://gisaid.org/">GISAID&lt;/a>에 들어가서 login을 클릭하면 sign up 창이 있다. 넘어가서 Register를 눌러준다.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/59f14604-5b30-43d8-8e47-00d897cc6fb2" alt="image" />&lt;/p>
&lt;p>GISAID 사용자 계정을 받기위한 개인사업자등록 양식을 작성해줘야한다.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/02049d8c-18a3-4784-b5c2-e16e36243678" alt="image" />&lt;/p>
&lt;p>입력한 이메일로 온 링크로 들어가면 이 화면이 뜬다.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/93aef75d-8bb1-4bc9-9d59-338483276013" alt="image" />&lt;/p>
&lt;p>아직 로그인은 안되는듯.. 왜냐면 비밀번호를 친적이없음 ㅠㅠ&lt;/p>
&lt;h2 id="0830">
 0830
 &lt;a class="anchor" href="#0830">#&lt;/a>
&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>계정생성 승인이 넘느린거같아서 그냥 연구실 계정을 받았다.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/2eab579e-e840-4b86-afc8-d752396baf4d" alt="image" />&lt;/p>
&lt;p>로그인을 하면 이렇게뜬다. 근데 내가 받고싶은 EpiFlu 빼고 다 클릭됨&amp;hellip;&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>[github] mac 터미널로 깃허브 디렉토리 내 모든파일 다운받기</title><link>https://yshghid.github.io/docs/bioinformatics/note/github/</link><pubDate>Mon, 19 Aug 2024 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://yshghid.github.io/docs/bioinformatics/note/github/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="github-mac-터미널로-깃허브-디렉토리-내-모든파일-다운받기">
 [github] mac 터미널로 깃허브 디렉토리 내 모든파일 다운받기
 &lt;a class="anchor" href="#github-mac-%ed%84%b0%eb%af%b8%eb%84%90%eb%a1%9c-%ea%b9%83%ed%97%88%eb%b8%8c-%eb%94%94%eb%a0%89%ed%86%a0%eb%a6%ac-%eb%82%b4-%eb%aa%a8%eb%93%a0%ed%8c%8c%ec%9d%bc-%eb%8b%a4%ec%9a%b4%eb%b0%9b%ea%b8%b0">#&lt;/a>
&lt;/h1>
&lt;p>&amp;ldquo;&lt;a href="https://github.com/heineman/LearningAlgorithms/tree/main/algs%22">https://github.com/heineman/LearningAlgorithms/tree/main/algs"&lt;/a> 디렉토리 내 모든 파일을 터미널 명령어로 다운받기.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;strong>방법1&lt;/strong>&lt;/p>
&lt;pre tabindex="0">&lt;code>curl -s https://api.github.com/repos/heineman/LearningAlgorithms/contents/algs | jq -r &amp;#39;.[] | .download_url&amp;#39; | wget -i -
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;p>&lt;strong>방법2&lt;/strong>&lt;/p>
&lt;pre tabindex="0">&lt;code>wget -qO- https://api.github.com/repos/heineman/LearningAlgorithms/contents/algs | jq -r &amp;#39;.[] | .download_url&amp;#39; | xargs -n 1 wget
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre></description></item><item><title>[알고리즘분석] coMethDMR</title><link>https://yshghid.github.io/docs/bioinformatics/note/algo1/</link><pubDate>Sun, 28 Jul 2024 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://yshghid.github.io/docs/bioinformatics/note/algo1/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="알고리즘분석-comethdmr">
